title: 62. A Pretty Home with Almost no Money- Chatting Thrifty Decor with Yami from "The Latina Next Door"
description:
I find myself constantly shouting it  from the rooftops, but you just don't need a whole lot of money to make a beautiful home. Yami proves it over and over again on her Youtube channel devoted to DIY and creating the look for less!
Follow along with Yami- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCR5WC5Z6kvm8oOz6iCwh8oQ
Her Ballard Designs "Look for Less" mirror- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0XyAAcFvE2Y
Check out her great room makeover- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0XyAAcFvE2Y
